  <brief_title>Risk Factors of Porphyria Cutanea Tarda (PCT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>“Factors Associated With Porphyria Cutanea Tarda in Patients Infected With Hepatitis C Virus”</official_title>
  <sponsors>
