  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of patients with documented PCT and HCV infection, documented PCT without HCV, HCV
      infection without PCT and controls without HCV or PCT.

      Single blood + urine sample uptake to investigate : mutations in HFE gene, uroporphyrinogen
      decarboxylase activity, HCV genotye, history of disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
